(37095, 81492, 3546, 1, 'Sunflowers', '', '2011-06-30 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 6, 'You’re circling around\nto find a shiny sunflower\nto taste her sweetness\nas you dive in lower\nYou’re like a busy bumble bee\nlooking for the pollens\ncan’t stop\nfantasizing of her\n\nGive her your T L C\nDon’t you flee, a loving seed\n‘cause that’s your only chance to make\nher feel\n\nnow just love her\ngo ahead you love her\nwith your gentleness\nlove her\nsay yes you’ll love her\nwith your foolishness\nThere is nothing like your tender loving care\nnothing like your tender loving care\nonce you love her\n\nShe’s driving you crazy\nnow you found that sunflower\nyou’re humming upside down\nto make your first encounter\nBut she has many bumble bees\nfalling under her powder\nwhy stop\nbe fascinated by her\n\n(Give her your T L C\nDon’t you flee, a loving seed\n‘cause that’s your only chance to make\nher feel\n\nnow just love her\ngo ahead you love her\nwith your gentleness\nlove her\nsay yes you’ll love her\nwith your foolishness\nThere is nothing like your tender loving care\nnothing like your tender loving care\nonce you love her)\n\nsunflower\nsoon you’ll have her\nsunflower\n\n\n你繞著圈圈\n尋覓一朵閃亮的 太陽花\n想感受她的甜美\n你逐漸接近\n像一隻忙碌的大黃蜂\n探訪著花粉\n無法停止想念她\n\n給她你的溫柔款待\n愛的種子別亂紛飛\n因為這是你唯一打動她的機會\n\n現在就愛她\n用你的溫柔盡情愛她\n好好愛她\n說你會盲目地愛著她\n沒有什麼比得過你的溫柔對待\n你的溫柔對待\n一旦你深深愛上她\n\n她讓你神經緊繃\n現在你找到了那朵完美的 太陽花\n你嗡嗡地左顧右盼\n試著展開你們的第一次接觸\n但她身邊有好多大黃蜂\n拜在她的甜蜜花粉中\n叫人怎不為她深深著迷？\n\n給她你的溫柔款待\n愛的種子別亂紛飛\n因為這是你唯一打動她的機會\n\n所以就愛她\n用盡你最大的溫柔\n好好愛她\n說你會盲目地愛著她\n\n沒有什麼比得過你的溫柔對待\n你的溫柔對待\n一旦你深深愛上她\n太陽花 \n很快你將擁有她\n太陽花\n', '', 278, '', 'Luet', 'Luet', '崔', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2011-07-11 09:31:35', '2015-03-12 13:47:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(37096, 81492, 3546, 3, 'I Don''t Care No More', '', '2011-06-30 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 3, 'I thought you were the one,  who''s pumping my heart beat. \r\nWell finally,  you''re just a man who cheats.\r\nLike a wild wolf,  your life was fun with no rule,\r\nWell finally,  you were making me a real fool. \r\n\r\nYou said you loved me,  a pretty girl in blue jeans,\r\nWell finally,  lies threw me in a deep ravine.\r\nGot a beer,  pretending you were still here\r\nWell finally,  it''s better you.re not near! \r\n\r\nI don''t care no more, don''t care no more, don''t care no more, say \r\nI don''t care no more, don''t care no more, don''t care no more \r\n\r\nThere was no moon tonight\r\nYou''ve got a chance to make it right\r\nBut finally,  we ended up in a pointless fight\r\nYou''re so wrong\r\nLove''s not a game,  it.s not a hunt \r\nAnd finally,  my broken heart could still be strong \r\n\r\nI don''t care no more, don''t care no more, don''t care no more, say \r\nI don''t care no more, don''t care no more, don''t care no more \r\n\r\nIsn''t this stunning\r\nWhen it''s unfolding\r\nA fib with honey is\r\neverything you ever gave me \r\n\r\nI don''t care no more, don''t care no more, don''t care no more, say \r\nI don''t care no more, don''t care no more, don''t care no more \r\n\r\n一度以為你是唯一讓我心動的人\r\n倒頭來，你是個背叛的男人\r\n如同野狼，你的生活刺激, 無拘無束，毫無規則\r\n倒頭來，卻讓我成為不折不扣的傻子\r\n\r\n你曾對個穿藍色牛仔褲的漂亮女孩說真心愛她\r\n倒頭來，那謊言讓我陷入萬丈深淵\r\n來杯啤酒，佯裝你仍在我身邊\r\n倒頭來，沒有你的日子，我活得更好\r\n\r\n『我發誓我會說，我說』\r\n\r\n我不在乎，不在乎，我不在乎了，說阿\r\n我不在乎，不在乎，真的不在乎了\r\n\r\n沒有月光的夜晚\r\n你曾有挽回的機會\r\n結果呢，我們卻在無端的爭執中結束\r\n你錯得離譜\r\n愛情不是遊戲，更不是狩獵\r\n不過到最後，我破碎的心卻更堅強\r\n\r\n『我發誓我會說，我說』\r\n\r\n我不在乎，不在乎，我不在乎了，說阿\r\n我不在乎，不在乎，真的不在乎了\r\n\r\n回想起來令人震驚\r\n整個過程逐漸清晰\r\n一場包著蜜糖的騙局\r\n居然是你曾給我的所有\r\n\r\n『我發誓我會說，我說』\r\n\r\n我不在乎，不在乎，我不在乎了，說阿\r\n我不在乎，不在乎，真的不在乎了\r\n', '', 202, '', 'Luet', 'Luet', '崔', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2011-07-11 09:36:15', '2015-03-12 13:47:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(37097, 81492, 3546, 2, 'Mon Chocolat Chaud', '', '2011-06-30 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 3, 'I’m walking down the street busy Champs Elysees\r\nDreadful winter reindeers hop over a sleigh\r\nthere’s Lois Vuitton, Giorgio Armani, Chanel\r\nThey don''t catch my eyes; they don''t ring a bell\r\n\r\nChristmas is around the corner\r\nSearching around, excuse my manner\r\nOo... ... au chocolat chaud\r\nOo... ... au chocolat chaud\r\n\r\nI’m strolling by the river Notre Dame de Paris\r\nSnow in the air it smells so free\r\nCathedral organ’s playing jingle carols\r\nMusic’s swirling penetrates the fashion apparels\r\n\r\nSanta Claus he’s coming to town\r\nLooking for this, how can I slow down\r\nCraving for mon chocolat chaud\r\nCraving for mon chocolat chaud\r\n\r\nStreet light’s blinking\r\nWhat are you dreaming for this curiously white Christmas\r\nFirewood’s crashing\r\nWhat am I wishing for when warming up in red pajamas\r\nCraving, I’m craving\r\n\r\nThey’re dancing in the circle splendent Moulin Rouge\r\nLovers are kissing, hugging, drinking in the lounge\r\nTuxedos, diamonds, perfume & high heels\r\nI don’t give a look, they don’t make me reel\r\n\r\nNorth star twinkles in the darkness\r\nPlease tell me where to find some goodness \r\nWarm & creamy, Warm & creamy, \r\nWarm & creamy mon chocolat chaud\r\nNow it’s ready, mon chocolat chaud\r\n\r\n\r\n巴黎熱可可\r\n\r\n走在繁忙的香榭大道\r\n寒冬裡麋鹿們跳上雪橇\r\n經過L.V、阿曼尼、香奈兒\r\n他們今天都引不起我的興趣\r\n\r\n耶誕節即將來臨\r\n恕我到處尋覓\r\n嗯～一杯熱巧克力\r\n嗯～一杯熱巧克力\r\n\r\n我漫步巴黎聖母院旁的河堤\r\n雪花的氣味在空氣中散發恣意\r\n大教堂裡傳出風琴演奏耶誕組曲\r\n音樂繚繞穿梭在眩目的時尚服飾間\r\n\r\n聖誕老人快進城來了\r\n我得加緊腳步尋覓\r\n期待我的熱巧克力\r\n期待我的熱巧克力\r\n\r\n街燈閃爍，你夢想著什麼？\r\n在這個白色聖誕中，\r\n壁爐裡木炭跳動，你的心願是什麼？\r\n穿著暖和的紅色睡袍，\r\n期待著～\r\n\r\n舞者在閃耀的紅磨坊裡圍圈舞動\r\n愛侶們在酒館裡小酌親吻擁抱\r\n西裝燕尾、美鑽、香水與高跟鞋\r\n今天我都不在意，全都相形失色\r\n\r\n北極星在黯夜中發光\r\n請告訴我往哪兒尋找那美好東西\r\n溫暖又滑順 ～熱巧克力\r\n溫暖又滑順 ～熱巧克力\r\n溫暖又滑順，我的熱巧克力\r\n剛出爐的，我的熱巧克力！\r\n', '', 205, '', 'Luet', 'Luet', '崔', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2011-07-11 09:41:14', '2015-03-12 13:47:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
